# Ugra Agents & Intelligence

## New agent checklist

1. Extend `IntelligenceAgent` (`core/intelligence/agent_runtime.py`)
2. Implement `execute(ctx: AgentRuntimeContext)`, not raw `invoke()`
3. Add prompt YAML in `prompts/{agent_name}/v1.yaml`
4. Register in `core/di/container.py` → `_create_agent_registry()`
5. Do NOT modify `IntelligenceOrchestrator`

## State management

```python
await self._set_state(AgentState.SEARCHING, user_id)  # publishes AgentStateChanged
```

## Reasoning for non-trivial decisions

```python
self._cognition.evaluate_vacancy_fit(user_id, job, memory, goal)  # auto-records
```

## Personality

Applied automatically in `invoke()`. Set audience via context metadata:

```python
metadata={"channel": "owner", "is_owner": True}  # Hunter
metadata={"channel": "email"}                     # Professional
```
